data.description: This charming 3 bedroom,2 bath split floor plan home is an excellent opportunity for those looking for a place to call home. Its vaulted ceilings and skylight give the home a bright and airy feel. With 2 living spaces, you'll have plenty of room to make memories with loved ones. The formal dining room is perfect for hosting dinner parties,while the breakfast bar is a great spot to enjoy your morning cup of joe. The spacious Florida room is a real highlight of this property & opens up to a tranquil backyard surrounded by lush trees, providing a peaceful retreat after a long day. The well-maintained backyard offers ample space for a garden & has a shed to store additional items. It's just a short ride from Orlando, Kennedy Space Center, & the beaches. This home has been lovingly cared for THERE IS A COMMUNITY PARK ON CINNAMON FERN BLVD.
